name: Astrajingga Arrival
description:
'Astrajingga Arrival'

The 1st part of 'Astrajingga Act' series.

Astrajingga, Son of Semar. A character from Indonesian puppetry folklore. As a son of Semar, and member of Punakawan. He has another name called 'Bagong' and 'Cepot'. 

Astrajingga usually shows as a humorous and straight forward person. In Indonesian puppetry, people would like to stay all night until Astrajingga shown up. Because, he will make people laugh and sometimes he gives religious advice about life but still in humorous way. 

Ken Dylan
2022
